overview: Vio has a dream to become an actress. Vio also took part in the casting and shooting as a hitchhiking actor. However, Rio, his girlfriend did not agree with that. The situation became complicated when Herman, the producer, tried to seduce Vio. Luckily, there is Bagus, a young man who has the same dream as Vio, who always accompanies Vio in living his dream. Will Vio and Bagus pass the casting and become successful actors?
title: Kesting Oh Kesting
